snippet.title: ✨Tokotoko - Wholesome Direct trailer
snippet.description:
✨ Tokotoko is an adventure game in Augmented Reality available on iOS and Android.

You help Hako – a young Tokotoko – in becoming an artist. Tokotokos are creatures from another realm where every individual is encouraged in becoming artists in their own way.

Some like painting, others prefer writing poetry or playing music. They are cute but like all artists, they have personality!

However, if you become their friend, they will never let you down.

http://tokotoko.io/
Insta : http://instagram.com/tokotokogame_
Face : http://facebook.com/tokotokogame
Twitter : http://twitter.com/tokotokogame_
